{"thig2.6:0.1":"Therigatha 2.6 ","thig2.6:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thig2.6:0.3":"Mettikatherigatha ","thig2.6:1.1":"“Kincapi khomhi dukkhita, ","thig2.6:1.2":"dubbala gatayobbana; ","thig2.6:1.3":"Dandamolubbha gacchami, ","thig2.6:1.4":"pabbatam abhiruhiya. ","thig2.6:2.1":"Nikkhipitvana sanghatim, ","thig2.6:2.2":"pattakanca nikujjiya; ","thig2.6:2.3":"Nisinna camhi selamhi, ","thig2.6:2.4":"atha cittam vimucci me; ","thig2.6:2.5":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig2.6:2.6":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thig2.6:3.1":"… Mettika theri …. "}